name: Danger Dingo #04 - Del, Restored and Renewed
description:
Del is Danger Dingo #04 in the Danger Dingo collection by @CuddleofDeath!

Del has fought many battles in the past. Many of those battles were wins, and only one was a loss. That loss came at a great price and left Del's face disfigured. 

Del was retrieved in a critical state and received an intense facial operation.

Del is now restored and renewed...but not refurbished.

*Does not come with a warranty!*
